#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Configure the `hero` REST client with the TLS configuration named `my-service-tls`."
msgstr "Configure o cliente REST `do Hero` com a configuração TLS denominada `my-service-tls` ."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Set up the `my-service-tls` TLS configuration, specifically the truststore with the CA certificate.\n"
"Ensure the path matches the one used in the Kubernetes _Deployment_ configuration.\n"
"The file is always named `service-ca.crt`."
msgstr "Configure o TLS `do my-service-tls` , especificamente o truststore com o certificado da CA. Certifique-se de que o caminho corresponda ao utilizado na configuração _do Deployment_ do Kubernetes. O arquivo sempre se chama `service-ca.crt` ."

#. type: Title ==
